                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In balloting in two meetings on November 3 (<gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>
                    (III/1), <hi rend="italic">Plenary</hi>, pages 378–380) the General Assembly
                    elected the following jurists to the International Law Commission: Messrs.
                    Shu-shi Hsu, Amado, Rau, Brierly, Scelle, Cordoba, Hudson, François, Koretsky,
                    Spyropoulos, Alfaro, Yepes, Khouri, Zourek and Sandström.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
